### Iegūst visus CourseInfo ierakstus
GET http://localhost:8080/api/course-info
Accept: application/json

###

### Iegūst CourseInfo pēc ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/course-info/{{uuid}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Izveido CourseInfo ierakstu
POST http://localhost:8080/api/course-info
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "course": {
    "id": "COURSE_UUID_HERE"
  },
  "courseVersion": {
    "id": "COURSE_VERSION_UUID_HERE"
  },
  "academicHoursTotal": 40,
  "lectureHours": 16,
  "practClassesHours": 8,
  "independentWorkHours": 16,
  "prerequisitesDescription": "Zināšanas informātikā",
  "goal": "Iepazīstināt ar datu struktūrām",
  "annotation": "Kurss par klasiskajām datu struktūrām",
  "assessmentForm": {
    "id": 1
  },
  "language": "lv"
}

###

### Atjauno CourseInfo
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/course-info/{{uuid}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "course": {
    "id": "COURSE_UUID_HERE"
  },
  "courseVersion": {
    "id": "COURSE_VERSION_UUID_HERE"
  },
  "academicHoursTotal": 42,
  "lectureHours": 20,
  "practClassesHours": 6,
  "independentWorkHours": 16,
  "prerequisitesDescription": "Pamata zināšanas programmēšanā",
  "goal": "Padziļināt izpratni par algoritmiem",
  "annotation": "Kurss ar praktisku ievirzi",
  "assessmentForm": {
    "id": 1
  },
  "language": "lv"
}

###

### Dzēš CourseInfo pēc ID
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/course-info/{{uuid}}
